content: This isnâ€™t so much a question as it is feedback. In the call trainings it might be nice to encourage callers to keep a little notepad/journal when they call; that way if they come up with lines or ways of phrasing things that they really like, they can keep reusing them. I also think we should put an emphasis on smiling before people start each call. People on the other end can really hear the difference. My two cents. Thanks.
Thanks, Steve.  These would be great suggestions for debrief.
